## Weekly content targets

| Channel | Frequency |
|---|---|
| Instagram Stories | 2 per week |
| Instagram Post | 1 per week |
| LinkedIn Post | 2 per week |
| Blog Article | Only when material has real depth |
| Newsletter | As scheduled |

---

## Maintenance

- Review and update channel guides when you find a format that works particularly well
- Save strong published pieces as reference examples for future sessions
- Adjust weekly targets if your capacity or strategy changes

